headline: NWSA's Q2 Earnings Coming Up: Time to Buy, Sell or Hold the Stock?
summary: News Corporation heads into Q2 earnings with revenues expected to gain 3.2%, flat EPS at 33 cents, and mixed segment trends across publishing, digital and ads.
